WEBVTT

00:01:37.464 --> 00:01:42.168
<i>Soon, this flight 210</i>
<i>will arrive on Venus.</i>

00:01:42.635 --> 00:01:46.506
<i>Some people may have</i>
<i>an allergic reaction to</i>

00:01:46.806 --> 00:01:50.343
<i>the floating plants used</i>
<i>in the terraforming of Venus.</i>

00:01:51.311 --> 00:01:55.415
<i>It has a chance of degenerating</i>
<i>into Venus-sickness</i>

00:01:55.482 --> 00:01:59.352
<i>so if symptoms appear,</i>
<i>please consult a doctor immediately.</i>

00:02:21.541 --> 00:02:23.143
Quiet down, everyone!

00:02:23.476 --> 00:02:25.845
Both hands behind your heads!
All of you!

00:02:25.912 --> 00:02:27.580
I-- I'll give you money!

00:02:27.847 --> 00:02:29.849
I don't care about the others.
Let me off...

00:02:29.916 --> 00:02:32.152
Anyone who makes a ruckus
ends up like him!

00:02:37.223 --> 00:02:40.193
Damn it, why did this have
to be the day...

00:02:40.627 --> 00:02:41.861
You over there!

00:02:43.363 --> 00:02:44.631
Hey!

00:02:46.199 --> 00:02:47.700
You listening to me?!

00:02:47.767 --> 00:02:49.736
You! Get up!

00:02:51.504 --> 00:02:52.438
All right.

00:02:52.505 --> 00:02:54.507
Quietly put both hands behind your head.

00:02:54.574 --> 00:02:55.875
Hey! Don't fall asleep!

00:02:55.942 --> 00:02:58.478
Who the hell do you think we are?!

00:02:59.312 --> 00:03:00.346
You!

00:03:13.226 --> 00:03:14.761
Whoops, sorry.

00:03:14.827 --> 00:03:15.728
That's enough!

00:03:17.864 --> 00:03:20.700
Enough of you, Ms. Bounty.

00:03:43.456 --> 00:03:44.457
Don't be silly!

00:03:45.291 --> 00:03:46.759
This is 5000?!

00:03:46.826 --> 00:03:48.561
Special price.

00:03:48.628 --> 00:03:50.964
That's not written anywhere up there!

00:03:51.231 --> 00:03:53.733
But it's not to normal
residential quarters.

00:03:53.800 --> 00:03:57.237
I'm asking you for a favor here.

00:03:57.303 --> 00:03:59.539
All the way out there
to the middle of the desert.

00:03:59.606 --> 00:04:02.308
Hey! Don't rip me off here!

00:04:02.375 --> 00:04:04.010
Wait a minute.

00:04:07.347 --> 00:04:10.316
-Make sure it gets there! Got that?!
-Hey, wait!

00:04:16.589 --> 00:04:17.924
{\an8}Thanks for the business.

00:04:18.324 --> 00:04:20.360
{\an8}-Hi.
-What?

00:04:20.426 --> 00:04:21.461
{\an8}My share.

00:04:21.527 --> 00:04:22.395
{\an8}Here?

00:04:22.462 --> 00:04:23.930
{\an8}I need it now.

00:04:30.770 --> 00:04:33.373
That's all you get.

00:04:33.439 --> 00:04:34.774
I know that!

00:04:34.841 --> 00:04:36.876
Depositing it at the casino again?

00:04:36.943 --> 00:04:38.745
It's better than a bank!

00:04:39.946 --> 00:04:41.614
She never gives up.

00:04:47.420 --> 00:04:49.355
I don't need any more pickpockets.

00:04:52.659 --> 00:04:55.495
Amazing. You're really amazing!

00:04:59.065 --> 00:05:03.036
You're the one that rounded up the
hijackers with some amazing moves, right?

00:05:03.303 --> 00:05:04.537
I have a favor to ask.

00:05:05.071 --> 00:05:07.507
Can you teach me how to move like that?

00:05:07.674 --> 00:05:09.776
Is it judo? Or kung-fu?

00:05:13.746 --> 00:05:15.682
Hey, wait a minute.

00:05:16.349 --> 00:05:18.484
I want to be strong, like you.

00:05:18.818 --> 00:05:19.919
You're an annoying guy.

00:05:19.986 --> 00:05:21.521
A no is a no.

00:05:21.587 --> 00:05:24.557
Oh, come on. Just a little.
Please, master!

00:05:25.024 --> 00:05:26.592
Please!

00:05:28.394 --> 00:05:29.896
Hey, wait a sec!

00:05:33.366 --> 00:05:35.001
What was that guy?

00:05:43.342 --> 00:05:46.546
Come on, just a little bit.
Think of it as helping me.

00:05:46.612 --> 00:05:48.614
You got a little bit of mercy in you,
right?

00:05:48.681 --> 00:05:50.683
I'm out of that right now.

00:05:55.521 --> 00:05:58.057
Come on, please,
it's not like you're losing anything.

00:06:00.626 --> 00:06:02.662
Quit it already?!

00:06:02.729 --> 00:06:05.131
Venus has a lot of helium
in the atmosphere.

00:06:05.398 --> 00:06:07.366
You can fix it quickly with some medicine.

00:06:15.475 --> 00:06:17.810
Come on, that's not fair! Man!

00:06:17.877 --> 00:06:20.146
You're the one that...

00:06:21.881 --> 00:06:23.549
That was just a throat drop.

00:06:24.650 --> 00:06:25.518
You!

00:06:25.585 --> 00:06:28.421
Oh! Hands-on training?

00:06:31.457 --> 00:06:32.625
You're...

00:06:33.159 --> 00:06:36.429
I'm Roco Bonnaro.
Nice meeting you, master!

00:06:38.164 --> 00:06:40.433
Our first income in a while.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:43.569
I'll feed you something good.

00:06:44.036 --> 00:06:46.773
This is all thanks to the mastermind.

00:06:47.607 --> 00:06:49.041
And next up...

00:06:55.948 --> 00:06:58.017
I'm telling you to not tense up!

00:06:58.451 --> 00:07:01.087
But you can't defeat enemies that way.

00:07:01.587 --> 00:07:04.957
The flow is more important, not power.

00:07:05.958 --> 00:07:07.660
You have to be like the water.

00:07:09.662 --> 00:07:10.530
You get it?

00:07:11.431 --> 00:07:12.698
Not one bit.

00:07:13.099 --> 00:07:14.634
That's what I thought.

00:07:14.700 --> 00:07:16.903
All right, come after me with a knife.

00:07:17.570 --> 00:07:18.471
You'll get hurt.

00:07:18.538 --> 00:07:19.205
Just do it.

00:07:23.075 --> 00:07:24.444
All right, here I come!

00:07:30.917 --> 00:07:32.752
What's going on?

00:07:33.486 --> 00:07:34.987
I'm not tensing up anywhere.

00:07:35.888 --> 00:07:38.124
I'm just using your excessive force.

00:07:38.791 --> 00:07:40.793
I control the flow of power...

00:07:41.727 --> 00:07:45.064
and to do that,
I have to relax the whole body

00:07:45.198 --> 00:07:46.966
to be able to react to any movement.

00:07:47.467 --> 00:07:48.501
Yeah.

00:07:48.968 --> 00:07:50.870
I become like water.

00:07:50.937 --> 00:07:52.004
Water?

00:07:52.839 --> 00:07:53.806
Yeah.

00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:56.142
Water can take any form.

00:07:56.809 --> 00:08:00.746
It can flow along slowly
or beat down aggressively, right?

00:08:02.782 --> 00:08:05.184
I don't know if I get it or not.

00:08:06.919 --> 00:08:08.688
You should take care of your elders!

00:08:14.527 --> 00:08:15.528
Here, hold this!

00:08:15.595 --> 00:08:18.998
Tonight. No, tomorrow night. At the
cathedral on the outskirts of this town!

00:08:19.065 --> 00:08:20.032
Hey, wait!

00:08:20.099 --> 00:08:21.968
There he is! Don't let him get away!

00:08:27.073 --> 00:08:28.241
Casino?

00:08:29.075 --> 00:08:31.777
The ones around here
are famous for being stingy.

00:08:31.844 --> 00:08:34.046
Don't worry about it. It's not our money.

00:08:34.614 --> 00:08:38.251
On top of it, she takes off like a bullet
and we don't know when she gets back.

00:08:39.185 --> 00:08:43.956
Hey, no use wasting time.
How about making some pocket cash?

00:08:46.559 --> 00:08:47.693
Piccaro Calvino.

00:08:48.294 --> 00:08:52.698
Usually a stingy little thief,
but went in big this time.

00:08:53.666 --> 00:08:56.102
Price is doubled if we get the whole crew.

00:08:58.871 --> 00:09:00.907
And these are the stolen goods.

00:09:00.973 --> 00:09:04.844
They make the remedy for Venus-sickness,
but apparently it's hard to grow them

00:09:04.911 --> 00:09:06.712
and they're worth tens of millions.

00:09:10.983 --> 00:09:12.118
Sorry!

00:09:19.258 --> 00:09:22.828
Shit, where did he go?

00:09:22.895 --> 00:09:24.797
Shit, he's sure good at running.

00:09:34.173 --> 00:09:39.679
I say we take it. I mean, it's worth
much more than nabbing that group.

00:09:41.280 --> 00:09:42.315
No, we can't!

00:09:43.082 --> 00:09:44.584
Hey, you thought for a moment!

00:09:44.650 --> 00:09:48.187
Idiot! It's better to not be involved
with dangerous stuff like this!

00:09:48.254 --> 00:09:50.122
It's okay if they don't find out, right?

00:09:50.790 --> 00:09:52.725
So, how much did you lose at the casino?

00:09:53.125 --> 00:09:54.093
What?

00:09:54.727 --> 00:09:57.630
I'll leave Piccaro up to you.
I'm going after Roco.

00:09:57.964 --> 00:10:00.132
Why don't you wait?
You're gonna see him anyway.

00:10:00.199 --> 00:10:03.202
They say that Lady Bounty only has bangs.

00:10:04.737 --> 00:10:06.205
You mean Lady Luck.

00:10:11.043 --> 00:10:14.313
<i>Remains of a shuttle?</i>
<i>Why in such a place?</i>

00:10:14.380 --> 00:10:15.247
Don't know.

00:10:15.314 --> 00:10:21.120
<i>There might be some weirdos that do live</i>
<i>out in the desert, but still...</i>

00:11:16.709 --> 00:11:17.810
Don't move!

00:11:27.353 --> 00:11:30.022
Don't move! Both hands up!

00:11:30.823 --> 00:11:32.158
I'm nobody suspicious

00:11:32.224 --> 00:11:34.794
That makes me sound
even more suspicious, doesn't it?

00:11:35.428 --> 00:11:38.064
Who are you? Why are you here?

00:11:40.299 --> 00:11:42.068
Answer me!

00:11:45.137 --> 00:11:46.005
Let go.

00:11:48.040 --> 00:11:50.443
I just came here to see Roco.

00:11:52.144 --> 00:11:53.245
You're Roco's friend?

00:11:53.312 --> 00:11:54.847
Huh? No.

00:11:55.414 --> 00:11:56.282
I'm glad.

00:12:09.228 --> 00:12:10.930
Hey, make sure you wash your hands.

00:12:10.996 --> 00:12:13.933
We can't find him, Boss.

00:12:15.267 --> 00:12:16.769
Hi.

00:12:17.837 --> 00:12:21.407
You know, it's all because
of those floating plants.

00:12:22.408 --> 00:12:25.478
Sometimes they send spores
that look like snow.

00:12:26.846 --> 00:12:31.417
Most people are fine,
but my body isn't and my eyes...

00:12:32.084 --> 00:12:33.085
Isn't it inconvenient?

00:12:33.352 --> 00:12:36.255
No. It's not a big deal
once you get used to it.

00:12:36.755 --> 00:12:37.456
Besides...

00:12:38.124 --> 00:12:40.326
Sometimes you understand
more when you can't see.

00:12:42.261 --> 00:12:44.964
-You'll get better, right?
-If I put money into it.

00:12:46.298 --> 00:12:50.302
I don't mind staying as is, but Roco...

00:12:51.437 --> 00:12:53.072
He cares about his little sister.

00:12:55.474 --> 00:12:58.077
Roco sent me this yesterday.

00:13:06.118 --> 00:13:09.121
Everyone says bad things about him

00:13:09.855 --> 00:13:12.424
And he seems to hang out
with some bad people.

00:13:12.491 --> 00:13:14.293
But Roco is a good person.

00:13:15.895 --> 00:13:18.864
I might be one of those bad people
he hangs out with.

00:13:19.465 --> 00:13:22.401
Maybe. Maybe you are.

00:13:23.102 --> 00:13:24.970
But you're different.

00:13:26.071 --> 00:13:27.373
I can tell.

00:13:28.841 --> 00:13:32.211
Both you and Roco
have something beautiful deep in you.

00:13:32.411 --> 00:13:34.246
It's hard to tell, but it's there.

00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:38.384
I can see it.
That's why I'm offering you tea like this.

00:13:48.460 --> 00:13:50.462
Something beautiful, huh?

00:13:51.931 --> 00:13:56.135
I probably lost that long, long ago.

00:14:16.188 --> 00:14:18.591
I want to see Piccaro.
Tell me where he is.

00:14:19.191 --> 00:14:22.394
What? I don't know who that is.

00:14:29.602 --> 00:14:30.636
Can you remember?

00:14:31.070 --> 00:14:33.072
I remember now!

00:14:33.339 --> 00:14:35.174
What did you just say?

00:14:35.641 --> 00:14:38.077
The price of a gray ash seed?

00:14:38.143 --> 00:14:39.345
I'm just asking.

00:14:39.511 --> 00:14:42.348
Don't be a fool.
Those things are like gems.

00:14:42.581 --> 00:14:44.583
You're lucky if you ever see one.

00:14:47.219 --> 00:14:50.990
Well, it might be difficult
to sell them once you get them,

00:14:51.390 --> 00:14:54.093
but I would say 8 million each.

00:14:54.393 --> 00:14:56.495
-You got some?!
-No

00:14:56.562 --> 00:14:58.297
Thought not.

00:14:58.364 --> 00:15:01.166
-How about Piccaro?
-Oh, just a little more.

00:15:01.233 --> 00:15:03.102
Don't screw up on your end.

00:15:12.544 --> 00:15:14.546
So, little Roco.

00:15:15.114 --> 00:15:17.616
You can be nice and tell us
where the pot is.

00:15:17.917 --> 00:15:20.319
If you don't want to tell us...

00:15:20.552 --> 00:15:23.289
Sorry. I dropped it.

00:15:23.522 --> 00:15:25.324
That ain't gonna work, is it?

00:15:33.432 --> 00:15:34.600
My little Roco.

00:15:35.067 --> 00:15:38.370
I've heard that you have a little sister.

00:15:38.437 --> 00:15:40.239
She has nothing to do with this!

00:15:40.306 --> 00:15:44.043
Oh, really? Then where is it?

00:15:44.343 --> 00:15:45.444
I-- It's

00:15:56.188 --> 00:15:58.557
I want to see Piccaro.
Tell me where he is.

00:15:59.191 --> 00:16:01.193
You don't have to be so sudden.

00:16:01.293 --> 00:16:02.594
Huh? Where did you say?

00:16:03.195 --> 00:16:04.730
I can't breathe.

00:16:32.558 --> 00:16:33.993
Yo.

00:16:35.394 --> 00:16:36.462
You're here.

00:16:37.129 --> 00:16:38.764
And I brought it, like you told me to.

00:16:39.698 --> 00:16:42.301
Sorry, but I snuck a peek inside.

00:16:43.068 --> 00:16:44.570
You know what it is?

00:16:45.504 --> 00:16:48.507
Gray ash. Something
spectacular unlike its name.

00:16:49.308 --> 00:16:52.611
I mean, it's 10 times the bounty
placed on all of you.

00:16:55.314 --> 00:16:57.416
You're a bounty hunter, aren't you?

00:16:58.784 --> 00:17:00.652
Are you here to nab me?

00:17:02.721 --> 00:17:05.024
Stella needs this, right?

00:17:11.163 --> 00:17:13.298
Run, or you'll be killed!

00:17:15.501 --> 00:17:18.637
What is this?! I was just
sent on some wild goose chase!

00:17:19.071 --> 00:17:20.339
Jet! Are you listening?!

00:17:28.414 --> 00:17:31.050
S-- Stop, please.

00:17:32.184 --> 00:17:34.053
The gray ash is back.

00:17:34.420 --> 00:17:36.755
Come on, let him go. I'm asking you.

00:17:36.822 --> 00:17:39.758
Sorry to make you deliver
it all the way here.

00:17:39.825 --> 00:17:41.427
I give my thanks.

00:17:44.363 --> 00:17:45.364
You!

00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:56.775
Get rid of him. Quickly!

00:18:01.246 --> 00:18:02.314
<i>Piccaro Calvino!</i>

00:18:02.681 --> 00:18:03.715
Stay still!

00:18:10.456 --> 00:18:12.424
Can't she be a little more elegant?!

00:18:16.562 --> 00:18:19.465
Don't kill them!
You trying to kill our bounty?!

00:18:19.531 --> 00:18:23.669
Bounty hunters?
Get that thing back, now!

00:18:26.839 --> 00:18:27.873
Roco!

00:18:49.294 --> 00:18:50.162
Roco!

00:18:57.336 --> 00:18:59.438
Shit! Idiots!

00:19:01.373 --> 00:19:04.843
<i>Really, you've caused me enough trouble.</i>

00:19:05.210 --> 00:19:07.479
Come on, hang on! You alive?!

00:19:07.546 --> 00:19:08.680
Hey!

00:19:10.682 --> 00:19:14.586
Master did you see that right now?

00:19:14.920 --> 00:19:19.158
Yeah. Don't speak anymore.
I'll call a doctor right now.

00:19:19.224 --> 00:19:19.892
Hey!

00:19:20.792 --> 00:19:23.228
I have a favor...

00:19:23.428 --> 00:19:25.364
In the music box...

00:19:25.797 --> 00:19:28.233
I know. Leave Stella to me.

00:19:28.667 --> 00:19:30.235
I trust you...

00:19:30.469 --> 00:19:33.772
All right, hold on. Now, don't die.
Don't die!

00:19:36.942 --> 00:19:42.414
Hey, if I knew you earlier...

00:19:43.749 --> 00:19:46.952
would we have been friends?

00:20:09.508 --> 00:20:10.375
Come in.

00:20:12.311 --> 00:20:12.978
Roco?

00:20:13.245 --> 00:20:14.413
It's you, Roco?

00:20:15.514 --> 00:20:16.582
I'm taking his place.

00:20:17.849 --> 00:20:19.451
You'll do. You know what?

00:20:19.885 --> 00:20:22.521
Roco got me some gray ash!

00:20:22.588 --> 00:20:23.689
And the operation fees!

00:20:24.223 --> 00:20:25.824
They told me my eyes will be better!

00:20:25.891 --> 00:20:27.659
Isn't it wonderful? What should I do?

00:20:27.726 --> 00:20:30.329
I want to see Roco first.

00:20:30.395 --> 00:20:33.799
So, tell him to come here right
now! To hurry over here!

00:20:37.502 --> 00:20:39.638
Did he get caught?

00:20:40.239 --> 00:20:40.973
No.

00:20:41.573 --> 00:20:43.609
Then why isn't Roco coming?

00:20:53.685 --> 00:20:54.686
He's dead, isn't he?

00:20:58.657 --> 00:20:59.524
I see...

00:21:01.526 --> 00:21:02.394
Stella.

00:21:03.395 --> 00:21:04.663
It's all right, leave me.

00:21:05.697 --> 00:21:06.832
I know.

00:21:07.299 --> 00:21:09.835
Roco died because he
did something bad, right?

00:21:10.936 --> 00:21:13.739
Please, leave me for today

00:21:20.012 --> 00:21:21.613
I...

00:21:22.781 --> 00:21:26.385
I never got to see Roco once
with my own eyes

00:21:27.786 --> 00:21:30.956
Hey, what was Roco really like?

00:21:31.523 --> 00:21:33.458
You know without looking, right?

00:21:34.426 --> 00:21:35.694
He was a great guy.

00:21:36.495 --> 00:21:37.863
Just like the one you knew...

00:24:07.512 --> 00:24:10.448
<i>Starting next week, Ed will appear.</i>

00:24:10.515 --> 00:24:12.050
<i>Wait, who are you?</i>

00:24:12.117 --> 00:24:13.952
<i>Let me introduce myself.</i>

00:24:14.019 --> 00:24:17.622
<i>Edward Wong Hau Pepelu</i>
<i>Tivrusky the fourth!</i>

00:24:18.023 --> 00:24:19.958
<i>-That's a long name</i>
<i>-Who the hell is this?</i>

00:24:20.025 --> 00:24:23.461
<i>I made that name up myself!</i>
<i>Isn't it cool?</i>

00:24:23.595 --> 00:24:25.230
<i>First, what do you mean "the fourth"?</i>

00:24:25.497 --> 00:24:27.833
<i>Next Episode: Jamming with Edward!</i>

00:24:27.899 --> 00:24:30.035
<i>So, anyway who is this kid?</i>

00:24:30.168 --> 00:24:31.703
<i>Watch it!</i>

